# License-restricted dataset artefacts. Meta Fair-Speech, CORAAL, and
# L2-ARCTIC forbid redistribution of any part of the dataset, including
# reference transcripts that would end up in per-utterance CSVs. EdAcc
# is CC-BY-SA so technically redistributable with attribution, but kept
# out of git by default for size. CommonVoice (CC-0) and Artie Bias
# (CC-0) per-utterance CSVs are fine and can be committed.
experiments/bias_pruning/results/per_utterance/*fairspeech*
experiments/bias_pruning/results/per_utterance/*fair_speech*
experiments/bias_pruning/results/per_utterance/*coraal*
experiments/bias_pruning/results/per_utterance/*l2arctic*
experiments/bias_pruning/results/per_utterance/*edacc*